applyFilterChanges.description: Callback called when the operator, column field or value is changed.

applyMultiFilterOperatorChanges.description: Callback called when the logic operator is changed.

columnInputProps.description: Props passed to the column input component.

columnsSort.description: Changes how the options in the columns selector should be ordered. If not specified, the order is derived from the columns prop.

deleteFilter.description: Callback called when the delete button is clicked.

deleteIconProps.description: Props passed to the delete icon.

disableMultiFilterOperator.description: If true, disables the logic operator field but still renders it.

filterColumns.description: Allows to filter the columns displayed in the filter form.

typeDescriptions.args: The columns of the grid and name of field.

focusElementRef.description: A ref allowing to set imperative focus. It can be passed to the el

hasMultipleFilters.description: If true, the logic operator field is rendered. The field will be invisible if showMultiFilterOperators is also true.

logicOperatorInputProps.description: Props passed to the logic operator input component.

operatorInputProps.description: Props passed to the operator input component.

showMultiFilterOperators.description: If true, the logic operator field is visible.

valueInputProps.description: Props passed to the value input component.
